---
title: Honey Thyme Pork Tenderloin with Roasted Potatoes & Broccoli
description: A honey glaze may sound like something that goes with dessert, but mild-tasting pork loves a sweet sauce too... especially one that has a few savory elements in it for contrast. In this recipe, you’ll be folding an extra-large drizzle of honey into a rich, savory pan sauce, then spooning it onto pork tenderloin (and the roasted potatoes and broccoli served alongside, if you like).
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/615db8f220008b2e0307f097-7cf15518.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/honey-thyme-pork-tenderloin-615db8f220008b2e0307f097-51192f02.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/honey-thyme-pork-tenderloin-615db8f220008b2e0307f097
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 560 kcal
